snippet: The Coast Guard plane crashed shortly before 5 p.m. on Thursday in Cresskill, N.J., and “landed in trees,” an official said.
abstract: Small plane belonging to the Coast Guard Auxiliary crashes in Cresskill, NJ, seriously injuring pilot and co-pilot.
lead_paragraph: The Coast Guard plane crashed shortly before 5 p.m. on Thursday in Cresskill, N.J., and “landed in trees,” an official said.

headline.main: Plane Crashes in New Jersey, Injuring 2 Pilots
headline.print_headline: 2 Pilots Hurt in New Jersey Plane Crash
